Package com.genesyslab.platform.configuration.protocol.utilities

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LinqConditions<T>
    Utility interface designed for usage with Linq for filtering and sorting of items in given collection.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CfgErrorCode
    Represents unpacked information from Configuration Server error code.
    Usage sample:
    CfgUtilities
    CfgUtilities class is intended as a container for and a point of access to a set of configuration data utility functionality.
    ConfDeltaUtility
    ConfDeltaUtility class is designed for creation and appliance of delta objects.
    ConfDeltaUtility.ConfIDComparator
    Comparator function for "CfgID" configuration structures.
    ConfDeltaUtility.ConfStructKeysComparator
    Comparator function for comparing of configuration structures by their key attributes values.
    Linq
    This class represents set of static methods for querying collections and DOM structures.
    LinqConditionIsElement
    Supplemental utility class for DOM Elements filtering.
    LinqConditionsAdaptor<T>
    Default(base) implementation of the utility interface for filtering and sorting of items in given collection.
    It is created as "interface implementation adaptor" to simplify creation of custom filters/conditions.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CfgUtilities.DstErrorEnum
